{"tid":1692343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰機上文宣","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:34:01.000Z","uid":257808,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"518c591e384e1f17e9d7671cfff235278c5448ed","tid":1692343,"uid":257808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"我係一個美國留學生既香港人<br />\n國泰未出賣香港人之前買左機票聖誕返香港<br />\n心想罷搭國泰但退唔到票又冇錢買另一張機票<br />\n所以想問下巴打們有冇辦法喺機上發夢/文宣<br />\n例如喺美國機場登機閘叫口號？<br />\n<br />\n印文宣派比其他乘客又可唔可行？<br />\n最緊要只係想有效地和理飛<br />\n而又唔會影響到更多國泰員工被炒<br />\n<br />\n利申：國泰一日繼續出賣香港人 都唔會再幫襯！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"97768206ee3a1a4f5693562f9f2510e3cdd4a00d","tid":1692343,"uid":52524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bcff9283f8cd02498464730a215858289550f6","tid":1692343,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"痴喺廁所"},{"pid":"cd40a55280d65642fa140ee910c84f8741d821b5","tid":1692343,"uid":227370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:50:17.000Z","msg":"我知有人做緊，可以多D人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5751f1decc33daa01aa0ec1831a63d33b71d1d","tid":1692343,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好揀最後排坐<br />\n然後排第一上機<br />\n每個位放文宣呀"},{"pid":"06eb7facc49b75c2e877d10b6f1c5757b9c5e960","tid":1692343,"uid":257808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30bcff9283f8cd02498464730a215858289550f6","tid":1692343,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"痴喺廁所"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"有諗過做連儂空中廁所，<br />\n但唔知會唔會加重低級員工工作量/壓力？<br />\n要對凖目標 國泰高層"},{"pid":"f288621909013ca675727b2e94933708062a7087","tid":1692343,"uid":14918,"like